=Overview=
Performs all sorts of sanity checks in a recipe.

=Usage=
  '''RecipeLint''' <recipe-file>

==Options==
* '''<tt>-h, --help</tt>''' - Show this help.
* '''<tt>--version'''</tt> - Show program version.
* '''<tt>-v, --verbose'''</tt> - Enable verbose mode.
* '''<tt>-t, --thorough'''</tt> - Perform thorough URL/file testing (don't use cache).
* '''<tt>-D, --quick-and-dirty</tt>''' - Cut some corners (don't download files, etc; not recommended).
* '''<tt>-W, --no-web</tt>''' - Fully offline operation (not recommended).

